  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="cta-section" aria-labelledby="cta-heading">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-content">
        <div class="cta-text">
          <h2 id="cta-heading">Ready to start your own journey?</h2>
          <p class="cta-subtitle">Join thousands of families who are already living their travel dreams</p>
          <a href="#newsletter" class="btn btn-primary btn-large">Get Your Free Visa Guide</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Mission Section -->
  <section class="mission-section" aria-labelledby="mission-heading">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-intro">
        <h2 id="mission-heading">Why I Share This Journey</h2>
        <div class="divider"></div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="mission-content">
        <div class="mission-text">
          <p>Because if you're looking for someone who's actually living the life you crave, you've come to the right place. My mission is to help families like yours ditch the status quo and design a life that fuels your soul.</p>
          
          <p>Here's the thing: fancy coaches with their picture-perfect lives might not resonate with you if your dream doesn't involve suburbia and keeping up with the Joneses. I believe in finding a mentor who aligns with your values and aspirations.</p>
          
          <p>This website is for rebels, dream seekers, and anyone who knows there's more to life than the ordinary. I'm here to guide you through the process of deconditioning, ditching old patterns, and embracing a life of wild, free adventure (families included).</p>
        </div>
        
